# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3601
translate pt_br a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_88d57a24:

    # "Emi's body shivers and shudders against mine, and I can feel her starting to lose her balance. It must be harder for her to keep steady because she's missing her legs."
    "O corpo da Emi tem calafrios e estremece contra o meu, e eu começo a perceber que ela está perdendo o equilíbrio. Deve ser difícil pra ela, não tendo as pernas."

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:3606
translate pt_br a3_emi_up_down_and_up_again_baca9a18:

    # "I steady her as best as I can, cupping my hands around her backside. It's firm and taut."
